cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

The paper is related to speech processing and neural networks. The most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with speech processing. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category. Additionally, the use of LSTM layers and feed-forward layers suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible category. Finally, the paper involves waveform modeling and generation, which could also fit under cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing).
